      <section eId="sec_CHC-1211">
        <num>CHC 1211</num>
        <heading>1211. Â Final decree at first hearing</heading>
        <subsection eId="CHC-1211__subsec_1">
          <num>(1)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The child was placed in the petitioner's home by an agency and the child has lived in that home for at least six months prior to the hearing for adoption.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CHC-1211__subsec_2">
          <num>(2)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The rights of the child's parents have been terminated pursuant to Title X or XI and the child has lived in the petitioner's home for at least one year.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=72683</p>
        </authorialNote>
